    "description": "《九域异传-金乌劫》是一款以《山海经》“海外西经”篇十日并出为故事背景的Roguelike单机卡牌游戏。本作在游戏中创新地融入了棋盘元素，给卡牌玩法带来了新的趣味和智力挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/6cbb61503b2a16cbe0ef4233e7e1ceac.webp?t=1689832867\" width=304 height=57 /></span><br>尧之时，天现异象，十日齐出，天下大旱，民不聊生。各类凶兽乘机倾巢而出，为祸世间。祭祀女丑推演得知，如今须击破五行大印，方可削弱太阳的威能。众氏族氏临危受命，救天下苍生于水火。然而真相却在最后揭晓……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/50993ac440de5c8127f69602cdb470ee.poster.avif?t=1689832867\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/50993ac440de5c8127f69602cdb470ee.webm?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/50993ac440de5c8127f69602cdb470ee.mp4?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/92284c2e843919c787a03a24438febd6.webp?t=1689832867\" width=304 height=57 /></span><br>·基于卡组构建和棋盘消除的策略游戏<br>·创新的棋盘模式给卡牌玩法带来新的趣味和挑战<br>·多角色多流派Roguelike牌库构筑<br>·独特的拼块组合收益加成系统<br>·自由丰富的随机事件探索<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/000f8fa50c272bab187d412ecb247a68.poster.avif?t=1689832867\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/000f8fa50c272bab187d412ecb247a68.webm?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/000f8fa50c272bab187d412ecb247a68.mp4?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/12cac3542d56c62abe210451618f8e69.webp?t=1689832867\" width=304 height=57 /></span><br>·主线五幕关卡，提供20+小时的游戏时间<br>·2位英雄，六套初始卡组<br>·36种技能属性各异的怪物<br>·150多张不同功效的卡牌<br>·近百种道具物品<br>·22个随机事件<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/b1ca4f457c11df675a06f901ee55cad4.poster.avif?t=1689832867\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/b1ca4f457c11df675a06f901ee55cad4.webm?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/b1ca4f457c11df675a06f901ee55cad4.mp4?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/2120fcc196213fce18b8c0e333c93b8b.webp?t=1689832867\" width=304 height=57 /></span><br>·丰富故事剧情内容<br>·更多英雄选择<br>·更多游戏模式开发<br>·添加创意工坊<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/784841dfced6ce3cda7d24bb9d471d05.poster.avif?t=1689832867\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/784841dfced6ce3cda7d24bb9d471d05.webm?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2214420/extras/784841dfced6ce3cda7d24bb9d471d05.mp4?t=1689832867\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩家QQ交流群：674689766，欢迎大家来和我们讨论交流哦",
